            . I am a servant to Robert Bryan, a <rs id="t18271206-115-viclabel602" type="occupation">tallow-chandler</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18271206-115-victim692 t18271206-115-viclabel602"></join>, of Wardour-street, Soho. On the 29th of November I went down the area of Sir John Richardson's house, for orders, leaving my basket outside; the servants told me I had lost something - I came up, and a jar of honey was missing; I pursued him - he put it down on some steps in Tavistock-street, and I took him.</p>
